1
00:01:03,190 --> 00:01:07,760
[A Prime Minister's Disguise]

2
00:01:08,160 --> 00:01:10,870
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:16,430 --> 00:01:18,300
I have a feeling that Huo Jingheng's drunken words

4
00:01:18,300 --> 00:01:19,690
were a bit strange,

5
00:01:20,310 --> 00:01:22,840
as if he deliberately said them for me to hear.

6
00:01:23,890 --> 00:01:26,539
Could he already know something?

7
00:01:27,820 --> 00:01:28,950
When did he find out?

8
00:01:29,740 --> 00:01:31,550
Was Ling'er being summoned to the palace

9
00:01:31,550 --> 00:01:32,960
just a coincidence?

10
00:01:38,370 --> 00:01:39,170
Yue.

11
00:01:40,170 --> 00:01:41,479
Go check if the pastries from the kitchen

12
00:01:41,479 --> 00:01:42,370
are ready.

13
00:01:42,650 --> 00:01:43,039
Alright.

14
00:01:43,039 --> 00:01:44,170
Yes, Your Highness.

15
00:01:52,130 --> 00:01:52,590
Ling'er.

16
00:01:52,590 --> 00:01:53,039
Chi.

17
00:01:53,070 --> 00:01:53,500
Come.

18
00:01:53,590 --> 00:01:54,250
Be careful.

19
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:55,289
Come.

20
00:02:00,500 --> 00:02:01,900
Was your journey smooth?

21
00:02:02,580 --> 00:02:03,840
It went very smoothly.

22
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:04,870
Someone came to escort me here

23
00:02:04,870 --> 00:02:06,070
as soon as I got off the carriage.

24
00:02:06,070 --> 00:02:07,150
But Chi,

25
00:02:07,280 --> 00:02:08,080
why did you suddenly call for me?

26
00:02:08,080 --> 00:02:09,610
Is there something urgent?

27
00:02:09,940 --> 00:02:11,350
I just want to ask you,

28
00:02:11,630 --> 00:02:13,870
do you still want to be the Empress?

29
00:02:14,400 --> 00:02:15,750
If you have feelings for someone else

30
00:02:15,750 --> 00:02:16,640
and you don't want to enter the palace,

31
00:02:16,640 --> 00:02:18,440
just tell me as soon as possible.

32
00:02:18,520 --> 00:02:19,660
I'll make other plans for you.

33
00:02:19,660 --> 00:02:21,860
Who could I possibly have feelings for?

34
00:02:22,210 --> 00:02:24,610
During these days
at the Prime Minister's Mansion,

35
00:02:24,610 --> 00:02:26,140
don't you have any feelings

36
00:02:26,530 --> 00:02:28,210
for Du Tianzhao?

37
00:02:28,630 --> 00:02:29,430
Feelings?

38
00:02:29,750 --> 00:02:31,150
Of course not.

39
00:02:31,400 --> 00:02:32,240
Are you telling the truth?

40
00:02:32,240 --> 00:02:33,570
Of course.

41
00:02:34,130 --> 00:02:35,920
Then what do you think of Huo Jingheng?

42
00:02:35,920 --> 00:02:36,920
His Majesty?

43
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,340
His Majesty

44
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,810
is a rare and brilliant ruler.

45
00:02:43,829 --> 00:02:45,280
He's accomplished in both civil
and military matters,

46
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,350
wise, brilliant,

47
00:02:46,470 --> 00:02:47,840
kind-hearted, benevolent,

48
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,150
naturally pure and good,

49
00:02:49,150 --> 00:02:50,610
and very trustworthy.

50
00:02:51,820 --> 00:02:52,870
Chi, what do you...

51
00:02:52,870 --> 00:02:53,890
think of His Majesty?

52
00:02:53,890 --> 00:02:54,380
Hmm...

53
00:02:54,400 --> 00:02:54,700
You...

54
00:02:54,700 --> 00:02:55,770
You think...

55
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:56,950
so highly of him?

56
00:02:58,880 --> 00:02:59,940
Then it's settled.

57
00:03:00,560 --> 00:03:02,680
Since you have feelings for him anyway...

58
00:03:02,680 --> 00:03:03,370
Yes.

59
00:03:03,430 --> 00:03:05,560
You won't mind switching back with me.

60
00:03:06,520 --> 00:03:07,450
Switching back?

61
00:03:07,750 --> 00:03:08,680
Starting today,

62
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:12,060
you'll be the one to get along with Huo Jingheng.

63
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,430
So soon?

64
00:03:13,920 --> 00:03:15,280
Are you planning to leave the palace?

65
00:03:15,280 --> 00:03:16,860
Are you willing or not?

66
00:03:17,240 --> 00:03:18,520
I am.

67
00:03:18,590 --> 00:03:21,270
But I think now is not a good time

68
00:03:21,430 --> 00:03:23,590
to switch back.

69
00:03:24,660 --> 00:03:26,430
It's better to act sooner than later.

70
00:03:26,430 --> 00:03:28,200
I've done all I can.

71
00:03:28,230 --> 00:03:31,500
The rest can only be done by you personally.

72
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,390
Everything you need is here.

73
00:03:35,390 --> 00:03:36,840
Just memorize it thoroughly.

74
00:03:36,840 --> 00:03:39,020
Records of Dog Huo's Daily Life?

75
00:03:40,450 --> 00:03:41,590
This log

76
00:03:41,750 --> 00:03:43,160
records all the details

77
00:03:43,190 --> 00:03:44,130
since I first entered the palace

78
00:03:44,130 --> 00:03:44,870
[Day 1: Huo Jingheng practiced martial arts at 5 a.m. to stay fit—fairly self-disciplined. At 9 a.m., he met with the court officials, attending to everything from national affairs to trivial matters.]

79
00:03:44,870 --> 00:03:46,460
and served Huo Jingheng at night.

80
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,470
You have to memorize it well

81
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,740
so you won't slip up.

82
00:03:49,430 --> 00:03:51,700
Trouble comes from the mouth.

83
00:03:52,130 --> 00:03:54,560
I shot myself in the foot.

84
00:03:54,910 --> 00:03:56,750
If Chi really leaves,

85
00:03:56,800 --> 00:03:58,550
what should I do?

86
00:03:58,770 --> 00:04:00,760
His comprehension isn't bad either.

87
00:04:00,760 --> 00:04:01,890
Given time,

88
00:04:02,650 --> 00:04:04,380
he could achieve great things.

89
00:04:04,680 --> 00:04:05,590
However,

90
00:04:05,620 --> 00:04:06,790
benevolence and righteousness to him

91
00:04:06,790 --> 00:04:07,230
[Day 2: He still practiced
martial arts at 5 a.m.]

92
00:04:07,310 --> 00:04:07,350
are like water to a boat.

93
00:04:07,350 --> 00:04:09,320
[At 9 a.m., he met with court officials,
keeping the people's well-being in mind.]

94
00:04:09,320 --> 00:04:10,700
They can either make him

95
00:04:11,290 --> 00:04:12,740
or break him.

96
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:16,779
But his benevolence and righteousness are misplaced.

97
00:04:16,779 --> 00:04:19,589
He's actually pretty cunning
when dealing with others.

98
00:04:19,589 --> 00:04:21,110
You know him well?

99
00:04:22,480 --> 00:04:23,340
Not really.

100
00:04:23,700 --> 00:04:25,130
Don't you remember, Chi?

101
00:04:25,430 --> 00:04:26,350
I met him

102
00:04:26,430 --> 00:04:28,330
when we were kids.

103
00:04:29,190 --> 00:04:30,480
I'm just

104
00:04:30,480 --> 00:04:32,590
guessing from the words

105
00:04:32,630 --> 00:04:33,740
in this log.

106
00:04:35,300 --> 00:04:36,409
Stop guessing.

107
00:04:36,480 --> 00:04:37,340
Memorize it well

108
00:04:37,340 --> 00:04:38,810
and get ready to serve him tonight.

109
00:04:38,810 --> 00:04:40,170
Serve him tonight?

110
00:04:44,180 --> 00:04:45,060
Consort Yue.

111
00:04:50,420 --> 00:04:52,380
Greetings, Your Majesty.

112
00:04:59,920 --> 00:05:00,800
Well then,

113
00:05:01,000 --> 00:05:02,330
Dear, keep me company again tonight

114
00:05:02,330 --> 00:05:04,750
while I go over the memorials.

115
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,000
The person who had been with him
for so many days

116
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:10,890
was suddenly replaced,

117
00:05:10,890 --> 00:05:13,420
yet he didn't notice anything unusual
at all.

118
00:05:13,950 --> 00:05:15,280
Something's not right.

119
00:05:21,120 --> 00:05:22,230
What should we do?

120
00:05:25,350 --> 00:05:26,950
Dear, look at this advice.

121
00:05:27,030 --> 00:05:28,390
It really speaks to me.

122
00:05:28,410 --> 00:05:29,810
Let's not make a move now.

123
00:05:33,770 --> 00:05:35,390
[Records of Dog Huo's Daily Life]

124
00:05:40,700 --> 00:05:42,950
My brother has fully prepared

125
00:05:43,170 --> 00:05:44,830
and is determined to succeed.

126
00:05:44,870 --> 00:05:46,070
What should we do now?

127
00:05:48,440 --> 00:05:49,170
Give it to me.

128
00:05:49,670 --> 00:05:50,990
I want to see it.

129
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:58,640
No matter how they try to fake it,

130
00:05:58,900 --> 00:06:01,810
the familiarity in those little details
can't be forged.

131
00:06:01,810 --> 00:06:04,840
The two of them have probably been
in contact in private for quite some time.

132
00:06:04,840 --> 00:06:06,110
To avoid any complications,

133
00:06:06,110 --> 00:06:07,310
I'll leave tomorrow.

134
00:06:10,350 --> 00:06:14,250
[Yongqian Palace]

135
00:06:14,390 --> 00:06:14,920
[Records of Dog Huo's Daily Life]

136
00:06:15,360 --> 00:06:18,110
[Day 1: Huo Jingheng practiced martial arts at 5 a.m. to stay fit—fairly self-disciplined. At 9 a.m., he met with the court officials, attending to everything from national affairs to trivial matters.]

137
00:06:23,980 --> 00:06:25,530
Dog Huo has injuries on his back.

138
00:06:25,530 --> 00:06:27,370
It hurts faintly when exposed to wind,

139
00:06:27,370 --> 00:06:28,970
so make sure to keep him warm.

140
00:06:29,420 --> 00:06:30,810
He prefers light food,

141
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,510
dislikes anything too strongly flavored.

142
00:06:32,510 --> 00:06:33,920
Steamed or boiled dishes
with minimal oil and salt

143
00:06:33,920 --> 00:06:34,770
suit him best.

144
00:06:36,350 --> 00:06:37,730
He is a man of benevolence
and righteousness.

145
00:06:37,730 --> 00:06:39,860
Perhaps I could marry my sister to him.

146
00:06:40,850 --> 00:06:42,170
In this world,

147
00:06:42,520 --> 00:06:43,890
there's no shortage of talented people
who can be generals and ministers,

148
00:06:43,890 --> 00:06:45,290
nor ambitious schemers.

149
00:06:45,840 --> 00:06:50,240
But it's rare to find someone who truly
values benevolence and righteousness.

150
00:06:54,820 --> 00:06:55,680
Chi,

151
00:06:56,409 --> 00:06:58,140
you're leaving already?

152
00:06:58,170 --> 00:07:00,650
I've memorized the log,

153
00:07:00,810 --> 00:07:02,990
but there's still this whole pile
of memorials.

154
00:07:02,990 --> 00:07:04,680
How can I handle them on my own?

155
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:06,120
Come on,

156
00:07:06,140 --> 00:07:06,980
Chi.

157
00:07:07,390 --> 00:07:08,160
I know

158
00:07:08,160 --> 00:07:09,950
you've always been the kindest to me.

159
00:07:09,950 --> 00:07:11,000
Please help me.

160
00:07:11,530 --> 00:07:13,260
Our Ling'er is capable of anything.

161
00:07:13,260 --> 00:07:14,510
You don't need any help.

162
00:07:14,510 --> 00:07:15,480
But...

163
00:07:15,910 --> 00:07:16,630
Ling'er,

164
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,380
isn't there something...

165
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,390
you want to tell me?

166
00:07:23,160 --> 00:07:24,190
No.

167
00:07:26,660 --> 00:07:28,570
By His Majesty's oral decree,

168
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,630
Consort Yue

169
00:07:29,630 --> 00:07:33,120
-is summoned to the Imperial Garden!
-Chi,

170
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,950
did you hear that?

171
00:07:33,950 --> 00:07:35,240
Here we go again.

172
00:07:35,240 --> 00:07:36,980
Every time I hear that, I get nervous.

173
00:07:36,980 --> 00:07:38,690
If I go out like this

174
00:07:38,710 --> 00:07:40,150
and slip up,

175
00:07:40,180 --> 00:07:42,790
it could lead to the execution of our entire Yue family.

176
00:07:42,790 --> 00:07:43,440
Don't be afraid.

177
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:44,440
Just go.

178
00:07:44,950 --> 00:07:45,950
If something really happens,

179
00:07:45,950 --> 00:07:46,950
I'll be long gone.

180
00:07:47,450 --> 00:07:48,760
Given his temperament,

181
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:50,810
he won't make things difficult for you.

182
00:07:50,810 --> 00:07:51,370
Go on.

183
00:08:03,640 --> 00:08:05,170
Greetings, Your Highness.

184
00:08:10,650 --> 00:08:13,330
You think I'm Consort Yue?

185
00:08:13,980 --> 00:08:15,830
His Majesty said you are,

186
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:17,060
so you are.

187
00:08:18,560 --> 00:08:21,350
Huo Jingheng really does know
how to use people.

188
00:08:22,350 --> 00:08:24,420
I hope he can win over my brother.

189
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,550
Alright.

190
00:08:29,750 --> 00:08:31,380
You must be tired
from following me around.

191
00:08:31,380 --> 00:08:32,220
Just take a rest here.

192
00:08:32,220 --> 00:08:33,380
Yes, Your Highness.

193
00:08:40,919 --> 00:08:42,510
My brother is really leaving.

194
00:08:42,510 --> 00:08:44,640
You'd better think of a solution fast.

195
00:08:45,510 --> 00:08:47,390
I've thought it through carefully.

196
00:08:47,390 --> 00:08:48,810
He cares about you,

197
00:08:48,840 --> 00:08:51,300
so he'll continue reviewing the memorials.

198
00:08:51,600 --> 00:08:54,200
As for whose hands they're
submitted through,

199
00:08:54,610 --> 00:08:55,980
it doesn't matter to me.

200
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:59,540
After all, "Consort Yue"
is still in the palace, right?

201
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:01,360
Listen to your own words.

202
00:09:02,080 --> 00:09:03,680
You're being unreasonable.

203
00:09:03,720 --> 00:09:05,920
Trying to burn bridges after crossing?

204
00:09:06,870 --> 00:09:08,720
Consort Yue, watch your words.

205
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,720
She didn't go home all night.

206
00:09:10,720 --> 00:09:11,870
She must be mad at me.

207
00:09:16,720 --> 00:09:18,050
They already switched?

208
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:20,150
Can this really work?

209
00:09:20,850 --> 00:09:22,590
Those two siblings are
obviously different.

210
00:09:22,590 --> 00:09:24,300
Is my nephew blind?

211
00:09:26,130 --> 00:09:27,260
Don't panic.

212
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,510
They've probably just met.

213
00:09:33,510 --> 00:09:34,350
Your Majesty,

214
00:09:34,750 --> 00:09:36,170
you may not care,

215
00:09:36,200 --> 00:09:38,360
but I don't want to waste
my precious youth

216
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,380
stuck in the harem.

217
00:09:43,080 --> 00:09:44,890
Aren't you a man of benevolence
and righteousness?

218
00:09:44,890 --> 00:09:46,920
Then help me out.

219
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,250
Think about it.

220
00:09:48,510 --> 00:09:50,770
Having him by your side would be so great.

221
00:09:51,080 --> 00:09:54,030
Talking to him all night would be
convenient and enjoyable.

222
00:09:54,030 --> 00:09:56,200
Sure, keeping him here might be
a bit troublesome,

223
00:09:56,200 --> 00:09:57,770
but once it succeeds,

224
00:09:57,970 --> 00:09:59,630
you won't lose out either.

225
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,270
Keeping him isn't easy.

226
00:10:01,710 --> 00:10:02,990
Let me think about it.

227
00:10:03,480 --> 00:10:04,810
So,

228
00:10:05,150 --> 00:10:06,200
you've agreed?

229
00:10:07,270 --> 00:10:08,670
But there's one more thing

230
00:10:08,670 --> 00:10:10,080
you must promise me.

231
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,780
Don't come to my place again tonight.

232
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:15,120
I'm not like you rough guys.

233
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:16,320
I can't stay up late.

234
00:10:16,910 --> 00:10:18,910
Last night was my first time serving you.

235
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,910
It really wore me out.

236
00:10:22,200 --> 00:10:23,200
Serving at night?

237
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:26,040
She was kept up most of the night?

238
00:10:37,360 --> 00:10:38,200
Imperial Uncle,

239
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,440
you're finally back.

240
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,480
Where have you been?

241
00:10:40,480 --> 00:10:41,600
The Empress Dowager summoned you
to meet her at 3 p.m.

242
00:10:41,600 --> 00:10:43,250
It's already past that time.

243
00:10:43,850 --> 00:10:45,790
Why do you look so lost?

244
00:10:46,030 --> 00:10:47,270
Hurry up.

245
00:10:47,550 --> 00:10:47,670
[Zhou Xiran,
daughter of the Grand Guard]
[Xie Yingran,
daughter of the Minister of Works]

246
00:10:47,670 --> 00:10:49,200
Now Heng has someone

247
00:10:49,270 --> 00:10:51,170
he cares about by his side.

248
00:10:51,390 --> 00:10:53,840
As his uncle, you should settle down too.

249
00:10:54,270 --> 00:10:55,720
Among so many beauties,

250
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:57,320
is there anyone you fancy?

251
00:10:57,700 --> 00:10:58,370
Sister,

252
00:10:59,740 --> 00:11:01,070
it's easy for you to say.

253
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:04,730
Is it that easy to find
someone you care about?

254
00:11:05,110 --> 00:11:06,240
Besides,

255
00:11:06,880 --> 00:11:08,370
even if I find her,

256
00:11:08,640 --> 00:11:10,300
does that mean she'll be mine?

257
00:11:10,350 --> 00:11:11,830
If heaven has feelings, it too grows old.

258
00:11:11,830 --> 00:11:13,470
From today, I, Du Tianzhao,

259
00:11:13,550 --> 00:11:15,080
will have no heart and no feelings.

260
00:11:15,080 --> 00:11:16,670
I'll be alone for the rest of my life!

261
00:11:16,670 --> 00:11:18,330
It's nobody else's business!

262
00:11:28,030 --> 00:11:30,150
What nonsense are you talking about?

263
00:11:30,200 --> 00:11:31,310
I think you need to be taught a lesson.

264
00:11:31,310 --> 00:11:32,340
[Auspice and Blessing]

265
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:34,340
Wake up, you fool!

266
00:11:34,370 --> 00:11:36,670
Who said it's easy to find your soulmate?

267
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,830
Heng

268
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,930
was single for many years

269
00:11:40,080 --> 00:11:41,650
before he found Consort Yue.

270
00:11:41,650 --> 00:11:41,770
[Auspice and Blessing]

271
00:11:41,770 --> 00:11:43,210
One day,

272
00:11:43,230 --> 00:11:46,200
you'll find that special someone too.

273
00:11:46,670 --> 00:11:49,310
My special someone was stolen by him,

274
00:11:49,360 --> 00:11:50,720
my dear sister.

275
00:11:56,040 --> 00:11:56,810
Chi,

276
00:11:57,970 --> 00:11:59,670
you're leaving right after dinner?

277
00:11:59,670 --> 00:12:00,990
In such a hurry?

278
00:12:01,170 --> 00:12:03,370
Huo Jingheng might come by again tonight.

279
00:12:03,370 --> 00:12:04,510
I'll give you two some space.

280
00:12:04,510 --> 00:12:05,300
No need.

281
00:12:07,080 --> 00:12:09,080
We have plenty of time.

282
00:12:09,150 --> 00:12:10,720
But you need careful planning

283
00:12:10,720 --> 00:12:12,420
before leaving the palace.

284
00:12:12,600 --> 00:12:14,060
Why don't you take it slow?

285
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:16,990
I've already planned it out.

286
00:12:20,050 --> 00:12:21,370
What's your plan?

287
00:12:22,390 --> 00:12:24,390
In the previous dynasty, a
favored consort loved fresh water.

288
00:12:24,390 --> 00:12:26,270
The emperor secretly ordered
a hidden canal

289
00:12:26,270 --> 00:12:27,600
to be built beneath the Imperial Lake,

290
00:12:27,600 --> 00:12:29,550
connecting the waterways in
the capital to the palace.

291
00:12:29,550 --> 00:12:30,810
I can swim through the Imperial Lake

292
00:12:30,810 --> 00:12:32,810
to get directly outside the palace.

293
00:12:34,910 --> 00:12:35,930
I see.

294
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,920
Let me verify

295
00:12:39,510 --> 00:12:41,700
if it's really what I think.

296
00:13:01,440 --> 00:13:02,600
So many flowers.

297
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,440
Yes.

298
00:13:07,120 --> 00:13:08,320
Marigolds.

299
00:13:08,480 --> 00:13:09,940
Greetings, Your Majesty.

300
00:13:12,480 --> 00:13:13,270
Your Majesty,

301
00:13:13,270 --> 00:13:14,620
are these flowers...

302
00:13:15,210 --> 00:13:16,790
all to be placed in the Imperial Lake?

303
00:13:16,790 --> 00:13:18,810
Consort Yue, you love flowers.

304
00:13:18,830 --> 00:13:21,450
I want to fill the lake and plant flowers.

305
00:13:23,370 --> 00:13:24,630
That's not necessary.

306
00:13:24,670 --> 00:13:26,220
It's too much trouble.

307
00:13:26,250 --> 00:13:28,700
I think this lake is fine as it is.

308
00:13:29,280 --> 00:13:30,230
Hmm.

309
00:13:31,260 --> 00:13:32,810
Then I'll listen to you

310
00:13:33,080 --> 00:13:34,280
and won't plant them.

311
00:13:39,990 --> 00:13:42,610
Dear, you're dressed quite uniquely today.

312
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:47,890
You can't leave anyway.

313
00:13:47,920 --> 00:13:49,640
Why don't you just stay?

314
00:13:49,920 --> 00:13:51,920
There is no hidden canal here at all.

315
00:13:52,510 --> 00:13:53,270
So it really is Ling'er who's been

316
00:13:53,270 --> 00:13:55,170
tipping off Huo Jingheng.

317
00:14:12,520 --> 00:14:13,670
You may leave now.

318
00:14:14,200 --> 00:14:15,020
-Yes.
-Yes.

319
00:14:18,190 --> 00:14:21,600
Your Majesty, are you planning
to live in Fengluan Palace?

320
00:14:26,790 --> 00:14:30,000
We love each other deeply

321
00:14:30,080 --> 00:14:31,480
and can't bear to be apart

322
00:14:31,970 --> 00:14:33,790
even for a moment.

323
00:14:34,270 --> 00:14:35,720
Huo Jingheng keeps setting traps

324
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:37,630
and pressing forward step by step.

325
00:14:37,630 --> 00:14:39,090
What exactly does he want?

326
00:14:40,360 --> 00:14:41,510
I just remembered

327
00:14:41,510 --> 00:14:43,770
you still have some memorials to review.

328
00:14:45,330 --> 00:14:46,220
Tonight,

329
00:14:47,270 --> 00:14:49,330
I don't want to review any memorials.

330
00:14:53,600 --> 00:14:56,030
Never mind then.

331
00:14:56,150 --> 00:14:57,690
Your Majesty, are there any

332
00:14:57,710 --> 00:14:59,030
difficult matters at court lately?

333
00:14:59,030 --> 00:15:00,620
The night is long.

334
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:02,440
Why don't we talk about them?

335
00:15:03,720 --> 00:15:04,950
Dear, weren't you the one who least

336
00:15:04,950 --> 00:15:07,210
wanted to interfere in politics before?

337
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:09,720
Tonight you seem quite open to it.

338
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:11,910
In ancient times, there was a ruler
who deceived his vassals

339
00:15:11,910 --> 00:15:13,510
just to win a beauty's smile.

340
00:15:14,030 --> 00:15:16,600
Now I'm getting involved
in politics for you.

341
00:15:16,750 --> 00:15:18,000
What is there to fear?

342
00:15:18,630 --> 00:15:19,510
Very well.

343
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,030
Oh my.

344
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:23,480
[Memorial]

345
00:15:23,480 --> 00:15:24,510
These are

346
00:15:24,510 --> 00:15:27,310
all the difficult cases
I encountered at court,

347
00:15:28,080 --> 00:15:29,360
and I've made notes on all of them.

348
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:32,630
Dear, why don't you discuss them with me?

349
00:15:33,270 --> 00:15:35,030
This is the first one.

350
00:15:36,220 --> 00:15:37,880
Dear, what are your thoughts?

351
00:15:58,730 --> 00:15:59,530
Your Majesty,

352
00:15:59,800 --> 00:16:02,060
it's time for the morning court session.

353
00:16:20,630 --> 00:16:21,510
Your Majesty?

354
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:22,790
Please rise.

355
00:16:25,050 --> 00:16:29,360
Shouldn't you be attending court now?

356
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,840
The morning air is chilly.

357
00:16:32,230 --> 00:16:33,630
I came back

358
00:16:33,750 --> 00:16:35,920
to give you an extra layer,

359
00:16:36,270 --> 00:16:38,000
but I didn't expect

360
00:16:38,030 --> 00:16:39,960
to find you leaving in such a hurry.

361
00:16:40,080 --> 00:16:41,410
Where are you going?

362
00:16:41,750 --> 00:16:43,960
I woke up and didn't see you.

363
00:16:43,980 --> 00:16:45,270
Unable to bear the longing,

364
00:16:45,270 --> 00:16:46,670
I caught up to take a look.

365
00:16:47,240 --> 00:16:49,120
If I could catch one more
glimpse of your back,

366
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,520
that would be enough.

367
00:16:54,440 --> 00:16:55,750
Even so,

368
00:16:57,000 --> 00:16:59,200
it's a bit reckless.

369
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:02,030
If you had walked too fast
and gotten hurt,

370
00:17:02,270 --> 00:17:04,000
wouldn't I have lost my helper?

371
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:05,599
Your Majesty, you're right.

372
00:17:06,310 --> 00:17:09,640
This helper is going back to work now.

373
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:12,480
Do you still have many
difficult cases left to review?

374
00:17:12,480 --> 00:17:13,720
While I'm away,

375
00:17:13,720 --> 00:17:16,240
you must protect Consort Yue well.

376
00:17:16,480 --> 00:17:17,480
-Yes!
-Yes!

377
00:17:20,109 --> 00:17:20,720
Go.

378
00:17:32,850 --> 00:17:33,610
Chi.

379
00:17:36,030 --> 00:17:37,110
You seem so happy.

380
00:17:47,230 --> 00:17:49,090
You don't want to enter the palace

381
00:17:49,490 --> 00:17:50,940
and marry Huo Jingheng,

382
00:17:51,770 --> 00:17:52,610
do you?

383
00:17:56,790 --> 00:17:57,480
Chi,

384
00:17:58,720 --> 00:18:02,170
actually, I didn't think it through.

385
00:18:02,350 --> 00:18:03,440
At first,

386
00:18:03,440 --> 00:18:05,270
I agreed in the heat of the moment.

387
00:18:05,270 --> 00:18:07,200
But after spending time with His Majesty,

388
00:18:07,200 --> 00:18:09,800
I realized I have no romantic
feelings for him.

389
00:18:10,510 --> 00:18:11,750
I'm sorry.

390
00:18:13,090 --> 00:18:14,950
I don't want to marry him anymore.

391
00:18:20,550 --> 00:18:21,880
I'm very disappointed.

392
00:18:24,590 --> 00:18:25,810
Ling'er, if you have any concerns,

393
00:18:25,810 --> 00:18:27,810
why can't you just tell me directly?

394
00:18:28,160 --> 00:18:29,200
To me,

395
00:18:29,240 --> 00:18:30,870
your feelings matter most.

396
00:18:31,680 --> 00:18:33,160
If there's even a trace of reluctance,

397
00:18:33,160 --> 00:18:34,560
you shouldn't marry him.

398
00:18:35,310 --> 00:18:36,830
No matter who he is,

399
00:18:36,830 --> 00:18:38,160
we don't care.

400
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:42,860
Chi.

401
00:18:45,400 --> 00:18:46,590
She's my own sister—

402
00:18:47,020 --> 00:18:48,440
how could I not spoil her?

403
00:18:52,030 --> 00:18:53,200
Since that's the case,

404
00:18:53,200 --> 00:18:54,460
we'll change the plan.

405
00:18:54,540 --> 00:18:56,220
I'll arrange for you to leave
the palace first.

406
00:18:56,220 --> 00:18:57,550
Once you're safe,

407
00:18:57,570 --> 00:18:59,570
I'll find another chance to escape.

408
00:19:00,480 --> 00:19:02,940
Then won't Huo Jingheng be able to keep him?

409
00:19:03,330 --> 00:19:04,420
What now?

410
00:19:07,070 --> 00:19:08,230
How about this?

411
00:19:08,260 --> 00:19:09,860
Let's discuss it a bit more.

412
00:19:10,400 --> 00:19:11,240
The longer you stay,

413
00:19:11,240 --> 00:19:12,680
the more trouble you'll face.

414
00:19:12,680 --> 00:19:13,640
Hurry and pack your things.

415
00:19:13,640 --> 00:19:14,770
Leave immediately.

416
00:19:22,310 --> 00:19:23,310
So many people?

417
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:24,160
Yes.

418
00:19:27,870 --> 00:19:29,160
Every time we're out, there are

419
00:19:29,160 --> 00:19:31,160
so many imperial guards following.

420
00:19:31,350 --> 00:19:32,830
How can we possibly leave?

421
00:19:32,830 --> 00:19:34,680
It's good that the imperial guards are here.

422
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:36,480
Chi can't run away now.

423
00:19:38,590 --> 00:19:40,050
Everything has its match.

424
00:19:40,110 --> 00:19:42,300
Only that person in the entire palace

425
00:19:42,320 --> 00:19:43,990
can keep Huo Jingheng in check.

426
00:19:43,990 --> 00:19:46,520
Looks like we can only use this way to get away.

427
00:19:47,130 --> 00:19:50,000
I have a bad feeling about this.

428
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,240
I am of humble appearance,

429
00:19:54,350 --> 00:19:55,730
without talent or virtue.

430
00:19:55,730 --> 00:19:57,030
Since entering the palace,

431
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:59,210
I've been blessed with the care
of His Majesty and Your Grace,

432
00:19:59,210 --> 00:20:00,940
for which I am deeply grateful.

433
00:20:01,070 --> 00:20:03,470
I dare not monopolize His Majesty's favor.

434
00:20:04,740 --> 00:20:06,760
I plan to use three months' salary

435
00:20:06,990 --> 00:20:10,510
to invite Yanshuang Opera Troupe
in the capital to the palace,

436
00:20:11,100 --> 00:20:13,700
and invite all sisters in the palace
to present their talents as well.

437
00:20:13,700 --> 00:20:16,100
Your Grace,
I humbly ask for your approval.

438
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:22,890
She's really pushing her luck.

439
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,170
Qu,

440
00:20:26,260 --> 00:20:29,830
Consort Yue asked the Empress Dowager
for rewards for the whole palace,

441
00:20:29,830 --> 00:20:30,960
giving us a chance

442
00:20:30,960 --> 00:20:33,240
to show ourselves before His Majesty.

443
00:20:33,480 --> 00:20:35,000
Isn't that a good thing?

444
00:20:35,960 --> 00:20:37,000
What do you know?

445
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,710
She's playing a strategic retreat.

446
00:20:38,710 --> 00:20:39,970
Now that she's in favor

447
00:20:39,990 --> 00:20:41,550
and already a consort anyway.

448
00:20:41,550 --> 00:20:43,480
Now that she has pulled this stunt,

449
00:20:43,480 --> 00:20:44,830
all the consorts in the palace are saying

450
00:20:44,830 --> 00:20:47,620
she's kind, dignified, and understands propriety.

451
00:20:47,620 --> 00:20:49,420
If His Majesty whimsically

452
00:20:49,450 --> 00:20:50,710
makes her the Empress,

453
00:20:50,720 --> 00:20:51,250
Then I...

454
00:20:51,720 --> 00:20:53,880
So what do you plan to do?

455
00:20:55,940 --> 00:20:58,380
Why her, of all people?

456
00:20:59,340 --> 00:21:02,250
I suppose Consort Yue is quite special.

457
00:21:02,880 --> 00:21:03,510
Bah!

458
00:21:04,310 --> 00:21:05,550
I'll make her realize

459
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:09,310
that no flower blooms forever.

460
00:21:17,480 --> 00:21:18,310
Hey!

461
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:21,310
You were once a princess.

462
00:21:21,750 --> 00:21:22,550
Tell me,

463
00:21:23,270 --> 00:21:24,590
what's so good

464
00:21:25,310 --> 00:21:26,980
about staying in this palace?

465
00:21:28,310 --> 00:21:30,350
As a consort,

466
00:21:30,920 --> 00:21:33,310
no matter how rich

467
00:21:33,830 --> 00:21:35,000
or how favored,

468
00:21:35,450 --> 00:21:37,980
you're still just a bird in a cage,

469
00:21:38,590 --> 00:21:39,680
a fish in a pond.

470
00:21:40,110 --> 00:21:42,910
It can't compare to the freedom of being by my side.

471
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:45,050
I won't force her to do anything.

472
00:21:45,240 --> 00:21:47,680
Why does she have to enter the palace?

473
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,180
Who are you talking about?

474
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,360
Whoever she is!

475
00:21:53,470 --> 00:21:54,650
Is it Ling'er?

476
00:21:56,750 --> 00:21:57,400
Yes.

477
00:21:57,510 --> 00:21:58,160
Yes.

478
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,050
What's your relationship with her?

479
00:22:00,050 --> 00:22:02,000
What's it to you?

480
00:22:02,740 --> 00:22:03,920
You like her?

481
00:22:05,380 --> 00:22:06,800
Let go of me!

482
00:22:07,920 --> 00:22:08,990
I'm warning you,

483
00:22:09,070 --> 00:22:09,980
stay away from her.

484
00:22:09,980 --> 00:22:11,160
Don't get involved with her.

485
00:22:11,160 --> 00:22:12,240
Ling'er and Yue Chi

486
00:22:12,310 --> 00:22:14,070
shouldn't get too close to anyone

487
00:22:14,070 --> 00:22:15,840
from your new imperial family.

488
00:22:18,580 --> 00:22:19,260
What?

489
00:22:19,680 --> 00:22:20,660
It's dangerous.

490
00:22:21,880 --> 00:22:22,890
Dangerous?

491
00:22:22,990 --> 00:22:23,850
For whom?

492
00:22:26,240 --> 00:22:28,060
Only by leaving the capital

493
00:22:28,400 --> 00:22:30,060
will they be completely safe.

494
00:22:31,070 --> 00:22:32,890
You crazy woman!

495
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:37,880
The commander has ordered

496
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:39,080
that you can't leave!

497
00:22:39,160 --> 00:22:40,350
Put down your swords!

498
00:22:40,350 --> 00:22:41,640
She's got a sword to my neck.

499
00:22:41,640 --> 00:22:43,180
Come protect me.

500
00:22:43,830 --> 00:22:44,480
Hurry, hurry.

501
00:22:44,480 --> 00:22:45,720
Let her go.

502
00:22:51,940 --> 00:22:53,010
Where's Dugu Xing?

503
00:22:53,270 --> 00:22:54,900
He's carrying out a secret mission under the commander's order.

504
00:22:54,900 --> 00:22:56,150
Secret mission?

505
00:22:56,200 --> 00:22:57,460
Something big has happened!

506
00:22:57,460 --> 00:22:57,790
[Notice] [Wanted]

507
00:22:57,790 --> 00:22:58,880
Look, look!

508
00:22:58,880 --> 00:23:00,750
The palace just posted a new notice.

509
00:23:00,750 --> 00:23:02,350
They're offering a bounty for rare flowers,

510
00:23:02,350 --> 00:23:03,480
with a generous reward.

511
00:23:03,480 --> 00:23:04,300
Look!

512
00:23:04,720 --> 00:23:05,340
Wow!

513
00:23:05,340 --> 00:23:05,790
[Notice]

514
00:23:05,790 --> 00:23:07,510
Looks like the palace is having
a flower appreciation event.

515
00:23:07,510 --> 00:23:08,230
Yes.

516
00:23:18,680 --> 00:23:19,270
Yue.

517
00:23:32,750 --> 00:23:33,660
Yue.

518
00:23:34,480 --> 00:23:36,110
Have you prepared everything I asked for?

519
00:23:36,110 --> 00:23:36,550
Don't worry, Your Highness.

520
00:23:36,550 --> 00:23:38,280
Everything is well-prepared.

521
00:23:40,070 --> 00:23:41,060
Be careful, Your Highness.

522
00:23:41,060 --> 00:23:42,030
Watch out for your dress.

523
00:23:42,030 --> 00:23:43,000
Walk slowly.

524
00:23:43,830 --> 00:23:45,210
It would be better if I didn't step on it.

525
00:23:45,210 --> 00:23:47,300
I'd like to see if they'd still dare

526
00:23:47,480 --> 00:23:49,430
to stare at me if my skirt fell.

527
00:23:59,690 --> 00:24:01,770
[Elegant Dwelling with Spring Grace]

528
00:24:06,550 --> 00:24:08,030
Consort Yue is here!

529
00:24:10,830 --> 00:24:11,560
Consort Yue.

530
00:24:13,310 --> 00:24:13,670
Why are you leaving so soon after arriving?

531
00:24:13,670 --> 00:24:16,090
[Elegant Dwelling with Spring Grace]

532
00:24:24,240 --> 00:24:25,720
Greetings, Your Majesty.

533
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:27,600
Greetings, Your Grace.

534
00:24:28,510 --> 00:24:29,480
I...

535
00:24:30,590 --> 00:24:32,880
feel ashamed facing all my

536
00:24:33,110 --> 00:24:34,470
beautiful sisters.

537
00:24:35,790 --> 00:24:37,990
Wouldn't it be a waste of all that effort

538
00:24:38,160 --> 00:24:40,590
you put into dressing up if you leave now?

539
00:24:41,110 --> 00:24:43,450
Yue not only is tall,

540
00:24:43,480 --> 00:24:45,090
but her way of walking

541
00:24:45,120 --> 00:24:47,370
also has a masculine charm to it.

542
00:24:47,480 --> 00:24:48,710
That's true.

543
00:24:49,160 --> 00:24:50,880
She's so strong,

544
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:53,030
and with this vibrant outfit,

545
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:56,320
it really enhances her presence.

546
00:24:56,880 --> 00:24:58,070
Alright.

547
00:24:58,070 --> 00:24:59,930
Stop discussing her appearance.

548
00:25:00,270 --> 00:25:01,640
Is it a tradition

549
00:25:01,640 --> 00:25:03,400
in every dynasty for the consorts

550
00:25:03,400 --> 00:25:05,830
to insult each other indirectly

551
00:25:05,830 --> 00:25:08,790
before the banquet?

552
00:25:09,110 --> 00:25:09,950
From now on,

553
00:25:10,160 --> 00:25:11,890
you should just throw hammers.

554
00:25:13,240 --> 00:25:14,110
Consort Yue,

555
00:25:14,500 --> 00:25:16,750
your outfit today...

556
00:25:18,400 --> 00:25:20,200
-is quite...
-is extraordinary

557
00:25:20,280 --> 00:25:21,620
and truly stunning.

558
00:25:28,920 --> 00:25:30,840
I've never seen

559
00:25:31,000 --> 00:25:33,010
my son shy before.

560
00:25:33,200 --> 00:25:35,540
Looks like I might

561
00:25:35,560 --> 00:25:37,120
finally get a grandson now.

562
00:25:38,440 --> 00:25:39,530
Alright, Mother.

563
00:25:39,640 --> 00:25:41,370
Stop saying that. Let's begin.

564
00:25:42,510 --> 00:25:43,510
Later,

565
00:25:43,590 --> 00:25:46,200
all the consorts will show their talents.

566
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:47,970
There will be quite a show.

567
00:25:48,300 --> 00:25:50,150
Watch how I escape later.

568
00:25:50,640 --> 00:25:52,840
I'd like to see what tricks you're up to.

569
00:25:55,800 --> 00:25:59,030
