General Dugu,

571
00:26:00,480 --> 00:26:01,920
did my brother say

572
00:26:01,920 --> 00:26:04,120
where we'll go once we leave the palace?

573
00:26:05,010 --> 00:26:05,660
He didn't.

574
00:26:07,640 --> 00:26:09,110
Didn't you ask?

575
00:26:09,130 --> 00:26:10,240
There's no need to ask

576
00:26:10,240 --> 00:26:12,100
when following military orders.

577
00:26:13,510 --> 00:26:14,350
I think...

578
00:26:14,370 --> 00:26:16,350
there's some misunderstanding

579
00:26:16,350 --> 00:26:17,830
between my brother and His Majesty.

580
00:26:17,830 --> 00:26:18,590
He

581
00:26:18,590 --> 00:26:20,070
actually doesn't want to leave.

582
00:26:20,070 --> 00:26:21,680
Why don't we call it off?

583
00:26:21,680 --> 00:26:22,270
My Lady,

584
00:26:22,640 --> 00:26:24,300
if you keep talking like this,

585
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:26,150
I'll have someone send you back.

586
00:26:33,920 --> 00:26:34,880
Bestow a peach blossom on her.

587
00:26:34,880 --> 00:26:36,750
Lady Lan, please take the flower.

588
00:26:37,790 --> 00:26:39,640
Thank you, Your Majesty.

589
00:26:39,960 --> 00:26:42,090
I can also perform sword dancing.

590
00:26:42,110 --> 00:26:44,830
May I offer you another dance, Your Majesty?

591
00:26:45,400 --> 00:26:46,640
Bestow her another flower.

592
00:26:46,640 --> 00:26:48,000
Another flower!

593
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:54,250
Consort Hui will present
the Swift Battle Breakthrough Tune.

594
00:26:54,640 --> 00:26:55,380
Bestow her a flower.

595
00:26:55,380 --> 00:26:56,110
What...

596
00:26:56,110 --> 00:26:57,220
what flower?

597
00:26:57,310 --> 00:26:58,660
But I haven't played yet,

598
00:26:58,660 --> 00:26:59,460
Your Majesty.

599
00:26:59,950 --> 00:27:01,160
Bestow a white peony on her.

600
00:27:01,160 --> 00:27:02,550
A white peony.

601
00:27:03,340 --> 00:27:04,510
-Peony?
-Peony?

602
00:27:04,970 --> 00:27:06,750
"Only the peony truly represents
national beauty."

603
00:27:06,750 --> 00:27:09,880
Could it be that His Majesty
has already made a decision?

604
00:27:12,560 --> 00:27:13,440
Your Grace,

605
00:27:13,880 --> 00:27:15,510
I have a unique skill as well.

606
00:27:15,820 --> 00:27:17,750
You must be interested.

607
00:27:18,960 --> 00:27:20,560
Consort Yue,
you want to show your talent too?

608
00:27:20,560 --> 00:27:21,830
What are you going to show?

609
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:23,110
Uprooting willows by the roots

610
00:27:23,110 --> 00:27:25,790
or breaking a big stone with your chest?

611
00:27:27,100 --> 00:27:27,690
Neither.

612
00:27:28,270 --> 00:27:29,470
Please wait a moment.

613
00:27:38,130 --> 00:27:40,160
This is our Yue family's secret technique,

614
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:42,310
called "Returning to the Source."

615
00:27:42,510 --> 00:27:44,400
Returning to the Source?

616
00:27:44,640 --> 00:27:46,420
What does it mean?

617
00:27:47,200 --> 00:27:49,960
May I borrow your hairpin?

618
00:27:51,070 --> 00:27:51,750
Thank you.

619
00:27:59,920 --> 00:28:01,640
Returning to origin

620
00:28:01,660 --> 00:28:03,420
and tracing the source.

621
00:28:04,270 --> 00:28:06,000
Returning to origin

622
00:28:06,070 --> 00:28:08,030
and tracing the source.

623
00:28:13,390 --> 00:28:15,940
This is the origin of this hairpin.

624
00:28:17,030 --> 00:28:17,830
That's right.

625
00:28:17,830 --> 00:28:20,550
This hairpin is made from
an entire piece of coral.

626
00:28:20,550 --> 00:28:21,790
It's very precious.

627
00:28:22,160 --> 00:28:24,030
I present it to you, Your Grace.

628
00:28:24,050 --> 00:28:25,550
I wish you longevity

629
00:28:25,720 --> 00:28:27,470
and blessings that last forever.

630
00:28:27,470 --> 00:28:29,100
Your Grace, look.

631
00:28:29,400 --> 00:28:30,820
What a wonderful item.

632
00:28:32,810 --> 00:28:35,450
This is the handkerchief I carry with me.

633
00:28:36,090 --> 00:28:39,770
Returning to origin and tracing the source.

634
00:28:41,310 --> 00:28:45,220
Returning to origin and tracing the source.

635
00:28:51,510 --> 00:28:52,590
Your Highness?

636
00:28:56,270 --> 00:28:57,130
Yue?

637
00:28:57,270 --> 00:28:58,350
How can it be Yue?

638
00:28:58,350 --> 00:28:59,550
She conjured up a person out of thin air.

639
00:28:59,550 --> 00:29:02,720
Your Highness, I was just making pastries for you.

640
00:29:02,920 --> 00:29:05,400
Why did I suddenly come here?

641
00:29:05,900 --> 00:29:06,700
That's right.

642
00:29:06,720 --> 00:29:09,440
This handkerchief was made by Yue.

643
00:29:10,550 --> 00:29:12,060
How amazing!

644
00:29:12,960 --> 00:29:15,640
Marvelous, truly marvelous.

645
00:29:16,270 --> 00:29:17,000
Consort Yue,

646
00:29:17,240 --> 00:29:18,620
may I try

647
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:20,640
your secret technique?

648
00:29:21,300 --> 00:29:22,200
Of course.

649
00:29:23,550 --> 00:29:24,360
However,

650
00:29:24,790 --> 00:29:27,050
today His Majesty is bestowing flowers.

651
00:29:27,510 --> 00:29:28,600
I'm thinking…

652
00:29:28,790 --> 00:29:30,640
why not let His Majesty try it first?

653
00:29:30,640 --> 00:29:31,550
Well said.

654
00:29:31,880 --> 00:29:33,400
Let him have a try.

655
00:29:34,200 --> 00:29:35,930
Dear, is this secret technique

656
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,440
for real?

657
00:29:37,680 --> 00:29:38,720
It is.

658
00:29:39,070 --> 00:29:40,330
Can it trace the source

659
00:29:41,000 --> 00:29:42,310
of anything?

660
00:29:42,350 --> 00:29:43,440
Yes.

661
00:29:44,030 --> 00:29:44,630
Very well.

662
00:29:49,030 --> 00:29:51,290
Your Majesty, you are the supreme ruler.

663
00:29:51,430 --> 00:29:53,830
Your wishes carry more weight
than ordinary people's.

664
00:29:53,830 --> 00:29:55,350
I fear that my single prayer

665
00:29:55,350 --> 00:29:57,010
may not be granted by the gods.

666
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:57,860
Therefore,

667
00:29:58,400 --> 00:30:00,030
I need everyone here to close their eyes

668
00:30:00,030 --> 00:30:01,370
and chant

669
00:30:01,510 --> 00:30:02,830
"Returning to the origin

670
00:30:02,830 --> 00:30:04,550
and tracing the source" with me.

671
00:30:04,550 --> 00:30:06,480
You may stop only when I say so.

672
00:30:06,720 --> 00:30:07,560
By then,

673
00:30:07,680 --> 00:30:09,480
your wish will manifest itself.

674
00:30:12,240 --> 00:30:13,480
Don't disappoint me.

675
00:30:28,310 --> 00:30:30,070
Returning to the origin

676
00:30:30,290 --> 00:30:32,180
and tracing the source.

677
00:30:33,310 --> 00:30:35,160
Returning to the origin

678
00:30:35,550 --> 00:30:36,960
and tracing the source.

