Returning to origin and tracing the source.

683
00:30:48,830 --> 00:30:52,270
Returning to origin and tracing the source.

684
00:30:58,550 --> 00:30:59,970
Play with me?

685
00:31:00,270 --> 00:31:01,310
Goodbye.

686
00:31:17,250 --> 00:31:18,890
Huo Jingheng.

687
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,200
Sorry.

688
00:31:28,780 --> 00:31:29,680
Yunqing?

689
00:31:36,010 --> 00:31:36,870
Ling'er?

690
00:31:37,350 --> 00:31:38,680
What are you doing here?

691
00:31:39,840 --> 00:31:41,300
How do you know we are here?

692
00:31:41,570 --> 00:31:42,570
Did you betray us?

693
00:31:43,230 --> 00:31:44,510
What are you talking about?

694
00:31:44,510 --> 00:31:45,440
That's not true.

695
00:31:47,810 --> 00:31:49,410
Ling'er, how did you get out?

696
00:31:49,810 --> 00:31:52,670
Didn't you enter the palace and become Consort Yue?

697
00:31:52,790 --> 00:31:54,070
Who told you that?

698
00:31:54,730 --> 00:31:56,120
I thought...

699
00:31:56,330 --> 00:31:58,540
you truly wanted to marry my nephew.

700
00:31:58,850 --> 00:32:00,510
I was upset about it all night.

701
00:32:00,520 --> 00:32:01,570
That's not important.

702
00:32:01,570 --> 00:32:03,840
I have something more important to do now.

703
00:32:03,840 --> 00:32:04,970
You should go first.

704
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,010
I almost forgot.

705
00:32:07,040 --> 00:32:08,310
I have something more important
to tell you.

706
00:32:08,310 --> 00:32:09,640
Jiang Yunqing ran away.

707
00:32:09,780 --> 00:32:10,610
What?

708
00:32:11,170 --> 00:32:11,930
Oh no.

709
00:32:12,080 --> 00:32:13,200
With Yunqing's temper,

710
00:32:13,200 --> 00:32:14,530
she might storm back in.

711
00:32:15,540 --> 00:32:17,100
General Dugu, what should we do?

712
00:32:17,100 --> 00:32:19,610
The commander ordered us to wait here to assist him in leaving.

713
00:32:19,610 --> 00:32:21,780
Let's stay calm and wait for his orders.

714
00:32:21,780 --> 00:32:23,380
We must not disrupt his plan.

715
00:32:23,680 --> 00:32:24,350
What?

716
00:32:24,400 --> 00:32:25,350
Yue Chi is leaving?

717
00:32:25,350 --> 00:32:26,610
That's not okay, is it?

718
00:32:32,250 --> 00:32:34,410
What on earth is Consort Yue up to?

719
00:32:38,330 --> 00:32:39,930
Once I kill Huo Jingheng,

720
00:32:40,030 --> 00:32:42,160
I'll take you out of the palace with me.

721
00:32:43,480 --> 00:32:44,610
Hurry up and go back.

722
00:32:44,750 --> 00:32:46,510
The Empress Dowager is here today.

723
00:32:46,510 --> 00:32:48,110
Even if Huo Jingheng steps in,
he won't be able to protect you.

724
00:32:48,110 --> 00:32:48,860
I want to leave,

725
00:32:48,860 --> 00:32:50,350
but I want to take you with me more.

726
00:32:50,350 --> 00:32:51,350
Don't be foolish.

727
00:32:52,350 --> 00:32:53,080
Consort Yue?

728
00:32:53,200 --> 00:32:54,860
Where did you go, Consort Yue?

729
00:33:29,750 --> 00:33:30,950
Your Grace!

730
00:33:31,590 --> 00:33:32,440
Your Grace,

731
00:33:32,510 --> 00:33:33,400
bed news!

732
00:33:33,640 --> 00:33:34,750
His Majesty was ambushed

733
00:33:34,750 --> 00:33:35,790
by an assassin in the Imperial Garden!

734
00:33:35,790 --> 00:33:36,740
What?

735
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:38,440
Eunuch Wang.

736
00:33:38,480 --> 00:33:38,880
Yes.

737
00:33:38,880 --> 00:33:39,310
Hurry

738
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:41,110
and summon the imperial guards!

739
00:33:41,110 --> 00:33:41,590
Yes!

740
00:33:41,830 --> 00:33:42,360
This way!

741
00:33:42,400 --> 00:33:43,440
Hurry, this way!

742
00:34:03,070 --> 00:34:04,400
Surround the Imperial Garden!

743
00:34:04,400 --> 00:34:05,060
-Yes!
-Yes!

744
00:34:17,469 --> 00:34:18,250
Mother,

745
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,440
why are you here?

746
00:34:19,440 --> 00:34:20,510
What do you think?

747
00:34:20,690 --> 00:34:22,150
Hurry up and go after them!

748
00:34:22,310 --> 00:34:23,440
Never mind, Mother.

749
00:34:23,670 --> 00:34:25,480
The banquet is meant to be a joyful occasion.

750
00:34:25,480 --> 00:34:27,739
Let's not let the assassin ruin our mood.

751
00:34:28,270 --> 00:34:29,510
Let's put this matter behind us.

752
00:34:29,510 --> 00:34:30,630
Put it behind us?

753
00:34:31,070 --> 00:34:32,980
I think you're intentionally letting them go.

754
00:34:32,980 --> 00:34:34,179
Over the years,

755
00:34:34,550 --> 00:34:35,590
you've always been lenient with

756
00:34:35,590 --> 00:34:37,670
the assassins who've infiltrated the palace.

757
00:34:37,670 --> 00:34:39,870
The palace has become a fighting arena.

758
00:34:40,190 --> 00:34:42,360
Have they shown any appreciation for your kindness?

759
00:34:42,360 --> 00:34:45,420
Have they hesitated when swinging their swords at you?

760
00:34:46,150 --> 00:34:46,800
I must take care of

761
00:34:46,800 --> 00:34:48,280
this matter today.

762
00:34:48,510 --> 00:34:49,840
Pass on my decree!

763
00:34:50,030 --> 00:34:51,560
Lock down the palace gates!

764
00:34:51,949 --> 00:34:53,210
Anyone who resists

765
00:34:53,510 --> 00:34:54,650
will be killed without mercy!

766
00:34:54,650 --> 00:34:55,360
Yes.

767
00:34:55,630 --> 00:34:57,630
Those who harbor, protect,

768
00:34:57,760 --> 00:34:59,380
or have connections with the assassin

769
00:34:59,380 --> 00:35:00,440
will be punished equally!

770
00:35:00,440 --> 00:35:01,030
Yes!
